msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"01"
msgid "These arrogant Englishmen... They have no idea what they’re in for."
msgstr "Estos ingleses arrogantes... No tienen ni idea de lo que les espera."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"02"
msgid ""
"There's no time for that. Our reinforcements are on their way, we just need "
"to cut the highway and delay them as long as we possibly can."
msgstr ""
"No hay tiempo para eso. Nuestros refuerzos están en camino, solo tenemos que "
"cortar la autopista y retrasarlos todo lo que podamos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"03"
msgid ""
"It seems like there's a gap between convoys. I don't see any more incoming "
"vehicles. We should try to take over that manor across the highway, looks "
"like a decent spot to hold. This is our chance."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay un hueco entre los convoyes. No veo más vehículos "
"acercándose. Deberíamos intentar tomar esa mansión al otro lado de la "
"autopista, parece un buen lugar para atrincherarnos. Es nuestra oportunidad."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"04"
msgid ""
"Richtig. We have secured the manor and cut their lifeline. It won't be long "
"before they come back. Our reinforcements should be here any moment now. "
"Soldaten! Dig in and prepare to hold your ground!"
msgstr ""
"Richtig. Hemos asegurado la mansión y cortado vuestra línea de suministro. "
"No tardarán en volver. Nuestros refuerzos deberían llegar en cualquier "
"momento. ¡Soldaten! ¡Atrincheraos y preparaos para defender vuestra posición!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"05"
msgid ""
"We have been reinforced by some Grenadiere, they have set up a forward post "
"by the highway."
msgstr ""
"Nos han reforzado algunos granaderos, que han establecido un puesto avanzado "
"junto a la carretera."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"06"
msgid "More of our Kampfgruppe has just arrived from the West."
msgstr "Acaba de llegar más gente de nuestro Kampfgruppe desde el oeste."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"07"
msgid "We've got some pretty strong guns with us now."
msgstr "Ahora contamos con armas bastante potentes."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"08"
msgid ""
"We've also got a radio vehicle and an artillery observer. If we lose him, we "
"won't have artillery support anymore."
msgstr ""
"También tenemos un vehículo con radio y un observador de artillería. Si lo "
"perdemos, ya no tendremos apoyo de artillería."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"09"
msgid ""
"There are British and American units all around us, I'm sure they will want "
"their highway back. Use the remaining time to set up defences. We must hold!"
msgstr ""
"Hay unidades británicas y estadounidenses a nuestro alrededor, estoy seguro "
"de que querrán recuperar la autopista. Aprovecha el tiempo que queda para "
"preparar las defensas. ¡Debemos resistir!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"10"
msgid ""
"Keep the radio vehicle concealed, if it gets damaged we will lose access to "
"artillery support."
msgstr ""
"Mantén oculto el vehículo con radio, si se daña perderemos el acceso al "
"apoyo de artillería."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"11"
msgid ""
"We can’t hold them anymore. They've got too many tanks! We need to fall back "
"and regroup.."
msgstr ""
"Ya no podemos contenerlos. ¡Tienen demasiados tanques! Tenemos que "
"retirarnos y reagruparnos..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/ger_officer/"
"12"
msgid ""
"Move all of your troops to the West we’re going out the way we came. There "
"isn't much time left."
msgstr ""
"Mueve todas tus tropas hacia el oeste, vamos a salir por donde hemos "
"entrado. No queda mucho tiempo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier1/01"
msgid ""
"Verdammt... That column stretches farther than I can see... Trucks, tanks, "
"everything..."
msgstr ""
"Maldita sea... Esa columna se extiende más allá de lo que alcanza tu "
"vista... Camiones, tanques, de todo..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier1/02"
msgid ""
"Should we go back and report? Command should know they've got a lot of tanks."
msgstr ""
"¿Deberíamos volver e informar? El mando debería saber que tienen muchos "
"tanques."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier1/03"
msgid "They've got reinforcements! Vehicles approaching from the East!"
msgstr "¡Tienen refuerzos! ¡Vehículos acercándose desde el este!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier1/04"
msgid "It's getting darker... Something's moving in the distance! Panzer!"
msgstr "Está oscureciendo... ¡Algo se mueve en la distancia! ¡Panzer!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier1/05"
msgid ""
"We are running out of ammo! We cannot hold them for too long! There's too "
"many of them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nos estamos quedando sin munición! ¡No podemos aguantar mucho más! ¡Son "
"demasiados!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier1/06"
msgid "Go back! I'll cover you!"
msgstr "¡Vuelve atrás! ¡Yo te cubriré!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier2/01"
msgid "They don't even expect us. Marching like it's a parade."
msgstr "Ni siquiera nos esperan. Marchando como si fuera un desfile."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier2/02"
msgid ""
"They don't seem to be paying much attention at all. We should eliminate the "
"patrols before we go in."
msgstr ""
"No parecen estar prestando mucha atención. Debemos eliminar las patrullas "
"antes de entrar."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier2/03"
msgid "They are running away!"
msgstr "¡Están huyendo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier2/04"
msgid ""
"The Grenadiers have already dug their foxholes on the North-East flank. We "
"should focus our defences around the main road."
msgstr ""
"Los granaderos ya han cavado sus trincheras en el flanco noreste. Debemos "
"centrar nuestras defensas alrededor de la carretera principal."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[narrators]/"
"ger_soldier2/05"
msgid "Incoming artillery! It's getting closer!"
msgstr "¡Artillería entrante! ¡Se está acercando!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[reinforcements]/"
"artillery"
msgid "Artillery fire"
msgstr "Fuego de artillería"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[reinforcements]/"
"skip_button"
msgid "Skip preparation phase"
msgstr "Saltar la fase de preparación"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[scenario_text]/"
"transition_time"
msgid "Half an hour later..."
msgstr "Media hora más tarde..."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[tasks]/task_01"
msgid "Cut the highway and take control over the manor"
msgstr "Corta la autopista y toma el control de la mansión."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[tasks]/task_02"
msgid "Prepare all-round defensive positions"
msgstr "Prepara posiciones defensivas en todos los frentes."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[tasks]/task_03"
msgid ""
"Do not let any British trucks reach the Northern end of the highway (at "
"least 3 your soldiers must survive)"
msgstr ""
"No dejes que ningún camión británico llegue al extremo norte de la autopista "
"(al menos tres de tus soldados deben sobrevivir)."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[tasks]/task_04"
msgid ""
"Fall back with all your forces to the West (at least 3 soldiers must survive)"
msgstr ""
"Retírate con todas tus fuerzas hacia el oeste (al menos 3 soldados deben "
"sobrevivir)."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[tasks]/task_secondary_01"
msgid "Keep the radio vehicle operational"
msgstr "Mantener el vehículo con radio operativo."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/[timer]/timer01"
msgid "Estimated time until another British convoy"
msgstr "Tiempo estimado hasta la llegada de otro convoy británico"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/name"
msgid "Cutting the Highway"
msgstr "Cortando la autopista"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/name_big"
msgid "Cutting the Highway"
msgstr "Cortando la autopista"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Even though our initial strike was a success we couldn't hold against a "
"massive amount of enemy armor. We had to retreat from this sector but the "
"battle is not over yet. Now we are able to count our losses, regroup and "
"strike the enemy even harder."
msgstr ""
"Aunque nuestro ataque inicial fue un éxito, no pudimos resistir ante la gran "
"cantidad de blindados enemigos. Tuvimos que retirarnos de este sector, pero "
"la batalla aún no ha terminado. Ahora podemos evaluar nuestras pérdidas, "
"reagruparnos y atacar al enemigo con más fuerza aún."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"hat’s a disappointment. Our last chance to cut the Allied spearhead has come "
"and gone, and now the allies are likely to reach Arnhem after all. We should "
"organize another attempt to take the road as soon as possible, failure is "
"not an option!"
msgstr ""
"Qué decepción. Nuestra última oportunidad para detener el avance de las "
"fuerzas aliadas se ha esfumado, y ahora parece probable que lleguen a Arnhem "
"después de todo. Debemos organizar otro intento para tomar la carretera lo "
"antes posible, ¡el fracaso no es una opción!"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/date"
msgid "September 26th, 1944 · Arras, Koevering, North-Brabant, Netherlands"
msgstr ""
"26 de septiembre de 1944 · Arras, Koevering, Brabante Septentrional, Países "
"Bajos"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/place"
msgid "Kampfgruppe Jungwirth"
msgstr "Grupo de combate Jungwirth"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_09_koevering/story"
msgid ""
"A few days ago, the British paratroopers in Arnhem retreated South across "
"the Rhine River, effectively putting an end to Operation Market Garden. \n"
"\n"
" All that remains of the original plan is the salient around Highway 69 "
"(Hell’s Highway), and the Allies are hanging on to it with everything they "
"have. \n"
"\n"
" Your unit is part of 'Kampfgruppe Jungwirth', which is in position near "
"Koevering, ready to attack Highway 69. \n"
"\n"
" If you succeed, the allies to the North will be trapped! Take the highway, "
"and hold it!"
msgstr ""
"Hace unos días, los paracaidistas británicos en Arnhem se retiraron hacia el "
"sur cruzando el río Rin, poniendo fin de manera efectiva a la Operación "
"Market Garden. Todo lo que queda del plan original es el saliente alrededor "
"de la autopista 69 (Hell's Highway), y los aliados se aferran a él con todas "
"sus fuerzas. \n"
"\n"
" Tu unidad forma parte del «Kampfgruppe Jungwirth», que se encuentra en "
"posición cerca de Koevering, listo para atacar la autopista 69. Si tienes "
"éxito, ¡los aliados del norte quedarán atrapados! ¡Toma la autopista y "
"defiéndela!"
